rrent joint position\r\ngazebo::math::Angle currentPosition = joint->GetAngle(0);\r\njoint->SetHighStop(0, currentPosition);\r\njoint->SetLowStop(0, currentPosition);\r\n~~~", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>This has been requested <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://answers.gazebosim.org/question/5153/can-we-lock-or-freeze-a-moving-joint/\" rel=\"nofollow\">multiple times</a> on <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://answers.gazebosim.org/question/5608\" rel=\"nofollow\">gazebo answers</a>. The function would set the high and low stops to the current joint position.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"o\">//</span> <span class=\"nt\">Get</span> <span class=\"nt\">the</span> <span class=\"nt\">current</span> <span class=\"nt\">joint</span> <span class=\"nt\">position</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">gazebo</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">math</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">Angle</span> <span class=\"nt\">currentPosition</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">joint-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">GetAngle</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">0</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">joint-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">SetHighStop</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"nt\">currentPosition</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">joint-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">SetLowStop</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"nt\">currentPosition</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-03-10T18:48:41.532525+00:00", "milestone": null, "updat